title: Maria's Boemboe Bali Warung
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A small restaurant in a simple building with outdoor seating of benches and tables with a view of the ocean Bali's Mount Agung. The menu has about 10 different vegetarian dishes on offer, most of them in the veg section, of which some may be vegan or can be made vegan; please inquire. Every dish is made-in-house to order and adapted to personal preferences when requested. Located at the very north end of the Main Road in Jungut Batu.
